        drf-sideloading
        =============================
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/drf-sideloading.svg
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/drf-sideloading
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/namespace-ee/drf-sideloading.svg?branch=master
